%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Kolhapur%2C%20Students%20Are%20Transforming%20Into%20Communal%20Mobs%3A%20Fact-Finding%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121550%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.09.59-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Kolhapur%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20districts%20in%20western%20Maharashtra%20are%20witnessing%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20In%20just%20two%20months%20(July%20and%20August)%2C%20over%20a%20dozen%20incidents%20of%20mob%20intimidation%20of%20teachers%20and%20school%20administration%20have%20come%20to%20fore.%20But%20more%20disturbing%20still%20is%20the%20constitution%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cmob%E2%80%9D.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20students%20who%20are%20suddenly%20transforming%20themselves%20into%20a%20mob%2C%20finds%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20put%20together%20by%20a%20group%20of%20women%20activists%2C%20who%20have%20come%20together%20under%20the%20umbrella%20%E2%80%98Women%20Protest%20for%20Peace%20(WPFP)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20WPFP%2C%20comprising%20gender%20rights%20activists%20and%20educators%2C%20travelled%20to%20different%20institutions%20across%20Kolhapur%20and%20the%20neighbouring%20districts%20of%20Satara%20and%20Sangli%20to%20understand%20the%20growing%20but%20disturbing%20trend%20of%20communal%20disturbances.%20The%20group%20has%20handed%20their%20report%20over%20to%20Kolhapur%20district%20collector%20Rahul%20Rekhawar%20early%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolhapur%2C%20known%20for%20its%20anti-caste%20legacy%2C%20right%20from%20the%20time%20of%20Shahu%20Maharaj%20(the%2019-century%20king%20known%20for%20his%20progressive%20anti-caste%20policies)%20has%20witnesses%20communal%20tensions%20in%20recent%20times.%20Many%20radical%20caste-Hindu%20organisations%20have%20got%20a%20strong%20footing%20in%20the%20region%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20communal%20tensions%2C%20including%20violent%20attacks%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20most%20recent%20one%20was%20in%20June%20this%20year%2C%20which%20was%20triggered%20over%20celebrations%20of%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20coronation%20day%20of%20King%20Shivaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dehumanising%20Gurus%20While%20We%20Grandstand%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fteachers-day-india-nep-ncf-muzaffarnagar%5C%22%3EDehumanising%20Gurus%20While%20We%20Grandstand%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20days%2C%20at%20a%20local%20engineering%20college%20named%20Kolhapur%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Gokul%20Shirgaon%2C%20a%20woman%20professor%2C%20was%20heckled%20by%20a%20group%20of%20students%20as%20she%20began%20to%20discuss%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%9Cgender%20discrimination%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20class.%20Statements%20like%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20are%20rapists%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20are%20never%20involved%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20riots%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBabri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20order%20of%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%9D%20were%20reportedly%20made%20by%20a%20group%20of%20students%20in%20the%20class.%20The%20professor%20interjected%20and%20tried%20correcting%20the%20students.%20%E2%80%9CRape%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20any%20religion%20or%20caste.%20Rapists%20have%20no%20religion%20or%20caste.%20Rape%20is%20the%20most%20heinous%20form%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20The%20students%2C%20feeling%20challenged%20by%20the%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%20filmed%20her%20lecture%2C%20edited%20it%20and%20put%20out%20doctored%20parts%20which%20would%20make%20her%20statements%20anti-Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20no%20time%2C%20the%20doctored%20clip%20had%20gone%20viral%2C%20and%20many%20local%20Hindutva%20groups%20came%20to%20the%20institute.%20The%20institute%2C%20in%20a%20knee-jerk%20response%2C%20sent%20the%20teaching%20faculty%20on%20forced%20leave%20and%20later%20insisted%20she%20apologise.%20The%20said%20professor%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20render%20an%20apology.%20On%20refusing%20to%20apologise%2C%20the%20professor%20was%20asked%20to%20work%20from%20home%20and%20join%20only%20in%20the%20new%20academic%20year%20that%20began%20end%20of%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121656%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.10.13-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121656%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.10.13-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121656%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.10.13-AM-300x190.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121656%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.10.13-AM-1024x649.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672254%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22761%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3Etransgender%20rights%20activist%20Sudha%20Patil%20speaking%20about%20intimidation%20in%20educational%20institutions%20to%20the%20Kolhapur%20District%20Collector%20Rahul%20Rekhawar.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Megha%20Pansare%20of%20the%20Shramik%20Foundation%2C%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20who%20led%20the%20fact-finding%20exercise%2C%20said%20that%20in%20most%20instances%2C%20the%20institutions%20take%20extreme%20actions%20against%20their%20teachers%20out%20of%20sheer%20fear.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20the%20teachers%2C%20like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20engineering%20college%20here%2C%20are%20not%20at%20fault%2C%20still%20they%20are%20sent%20away%20just%20to%20dissipate%20the%20anger%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20behaviour%20is%20evident%20in%20over%2010%20cases%20that%20the%20team%20studied%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20report.%20Another%20such%20instance%20mentioned%20in%20the%20report%20is%20of%20the%20Seventh-day%20Adventist%20School%20in%20Kolhapur.%20On%20August%204%2C%20a%20student%2C%20appearing%20for%20an%20exam%2C%20wrote%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20on%20his%20answer%20sheet.%20The%20invigilator%2C%20following%20the%20strict%20exam%20rule%2C%20told%20the%20student%20that%20such%20a%20religious%20marker%20on%20an%20answer%20sheet%20was%20not%20allowed.%20This%20allegedly%20agitated%20the%20student%20and%20he%20tried%20to%20instigate%20other%20students%20to%20scribble%20similar%20words%20on%20their%20answer%20sheets.%20In%20no%20time%2C%20the%20student%20was%20able%20to%20mobilise%2040-50%20more%20people%20outside%20the%20school%2C%20who%20chanted%20slogans%20and%20barged%20into%20the%20school%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20soon%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20a%20local%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%20MLA%20intervened.%20The%20school%20management%20here%20did%20not%20take%20an%20adverse%20action%20against%20the%20teacher%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20take%20any%20action%20against%20the%20unruly%20student%20either%2C%20the%20report%20points%20out.%20The%20same%20school%20had%20another%20reported%20incident%20where%20a%20cleaning%20staffer%2C%20belonging%20to%20the%20Christian%20community%2C%20was%20bullied%20into%20chanting%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20radical%20Hindu%20outfits%20have%20mushroomed%20in%20the%20region%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20These%20organisations%2C%20Pansare%20points%20out%2C%20organically%20mobilise%20people%20and%20then%20hold%20a%20strong%20grip%2C%C2%A0particularly%20on%20the%20youth%2C%20through%20social%20media.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20riots%20broke%20out%20in%20June%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20many%20youths%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20violence%20were%20known%20to%20each%20other%20only%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20messages%20circulated%20on%20WhatsApp%20almost%20acts%20like%20a%20clarion%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121742%2FDSC_2260.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121742%2FDSC_2260.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121742%2FDSC_2260-300x174.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121742%2FDSC_2260-1024x595.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672255%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESaroj%20Patil%2C%20Megha%20Pansare%2C%20Meena%20Seshu%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Women%20Protest%20for%20Peace%20present%20a%20fact%20finding%20report%20%E2%80%9CInciting%20disharmony%20in%20educational%20institutions%20in%20Western%20Maharashtra%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Kolhapur%20District%20Collector%20Rahul%20Rekhawar%20on%20Sept%207%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intolerance%20of%20these%20Hindu%20outfits%20is%20palpable%20and%20both%20the%20college%20and%20district%20administration%20have%20given%20in%20to%20their%20pressure.%20At%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20College%20in%20Satara%20recently%2C%20a%20guest%20speaker%20talked%20about%20Govind%20Pansare%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EWho%20was%20Shivaji%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3EPansare%20is%20one%20of%20the%20four%20rationalists%20to%20be%20killed%20allegedly%20by%20Hindutva%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20had%20read%20the%20title%20of%20the%20book%20without%20suffixing%20Shivaji%E2%80%99s%20name%20with%20%E2%80%9CRaje%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CMaharaj%E2%80%9D%20(both%20means%20king%20in%20Marathi)%2C%20and%20local%20villagers%20had%20protested%20against%20the%20speaker.%20Along%20with%20the%20speaker%2C%20a%20school%20teacher%20was%20targeted%20too.%20When%20the%20teacher%20refused%20to%20apologise%2C%20the%20local%20police%20asked%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdisciplinary%20action%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20initiated%20against%20her.%20The%20college%20has%20forwarded%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20administration%20against%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22When%20Hate%20Fills%20Every%20Corner%2C%20From%20Classroom%20to%20Prayer%20Room%2C%20Where%20Do%20You%20Look%20for%20Hope%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuzaffarnagar-slapping-hate-hope%5C%22%3EWhen%20Hate%20Fills%20Every%20Corner%2C%20From%20Classroom%20to%20Prayer%20Room%2C%20Where%20Do%20You%20Look%20for%20Hope%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20schools%20and%20colleges%20too%2C%20mobilisation%20of%20a%20mob%20happens%20through%20social%20media.%20The%20report%20identifies%20multiple%20instances%20where%20doctored%20videos%20are%20instantly%20circulated%20on%20these%20social%20media%20groups%20and%20in%20no%20time%2C%20they%20have%20gone%20viral.%20Like%20it%20happened%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Chandrabai-Shantappa%20Shendure%20College%20in%20Hupari%20village%20in%20Kolhapur.%20Soon%20after%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20president%20Prakash%20Ambedkar%20visited%20Aurangazeb%E2%80%99s%20tomb%20in%20June%20this%20year%2C%20a%20lecturer%20at%20Shendure%20college%20had%20written%20a%20social%20media%20post%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Csince%20injustice%20is%20being%20done%20to%20both%20the%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%2C%20they%20should%20unite%E2%80%9D.%20This%20post%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20the%20villagers%2C%20garnering%20a%20negative%20response%20across%20social%20media%20platforms.%20The%20lecturer%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20mob%20and%20the%20police%20were%20pressurised%20to%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20him.%20On%20pressure%20from%20the%20villagers%20and%20other%20Hindu%20organisations%2C%20he%20was%20eventually%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20submit%20the%20report%20to%20the%20district%20collector%2C%20over%2060-70%20women%20had%20gathered.%20Some%20representing%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20groups%2C%20some%20as%20trans%20rights%20activists%20and%20some%20belonging%20to%20the%20minority%20communities%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20meeting.%20The%20group%20urged%20the%20collector%20to%20put%20down%20a%20protocol%20in%20case%20of%20such%20incidents%20in%20the%20future.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20a%20vitiated%20atmosphere%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20the%20educational%20institutions%2C%20the%20teachers%20(who%20are%20invariably%20at%20the%20receiving%20end)%2C%20and%20the%20police%20have%20a%20clear%20protocol%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20issues%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pansare%20said%2C%20explaining%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Shramik%20Foundation%2C%20members%20of%20rights%20organisations%20like%20Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samithi%2C%20Sangram%20Sanstha%2C%20Andha%20Sradha%20Nirmulan%20Samithi%2C%20Muskan%20and%20Maharashtra%20Minority%20Christian%20Development%20Council%20among%20others%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20discussion%20with%20the%20district%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694242319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09121550%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-09-at-11.09.59-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fin-kolhapur-students-are-transforming-into-communal-mobs-fact-finding-team%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20educational%20institutions%20across%20Kolhapur%20have%20seen%20communal%20tensions%2