high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20milestones%20are%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20many%20emerging-market%20peers%2C%20not%20least%20to%20neighbouring%20China%2C%20whose%20economic%20woes%20and%20struggling%20financial%20markets%20have%20become%20a%20source%20of%20frustration%20for%20global%20investors.%20In%20fact%2C%20troubles%20at%20its%20biggest%20EM%20rival%20have%20only%20burnished%20India's%20appeal.%20Developing-market%20money%20managers%20are%20now%20most%20overweight%20on%20India%20in%20their%20Asia%20portfolios%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20place%20to%20hide%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20China%20ranks%20among%20their%20largest%20underweights%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Group%20Inc.%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20report%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrong%20domestic%20growth%20prospects%2C%20ongoing%20policy%20reforms%20as%20well%20as%20robust%20credit%20growth%20are%20tailwinds%20contributing%20to%20the%20outperformance%20of%20Indian%20equities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Audrey%20Goh%2C%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Standard%20Chartered%20Bank%20SG%20Ltd.%20%26quot%3BThe%20shift%20to%20a%20multi-polar%20world%20would%20also%20likely%20benefit%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20government%20moving%20to%20make%20doing%20business%20in%20India%20more%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20stock%20market%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20valuation%20of%20%243.8%20trillion%20this%20week%2C%20a%20perfectly%20timed%20billboard%20for%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20G-20%20summit%20gives%20him%20another%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20the%20nation's%20potential%20as%20a%20geopolitical%20juggernaut.%20With%20the%20West%20looking%20to%20curb%20China's%20influence%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20rolled%20out%20a%20mix%20of%20tariffs%20and%20incentives%20to%20lure%20companies%20to%20make%20in%20India%20and%20firms%20including%20Apple%20Inc.%20and%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20are%20among%20those%20expanding%20production%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20investors%20have%20bought%20more%20than%20%2416%20billion%20worth%20of%20Indian%20stocks%20on%20a%20net%20basis%20so%20far%20in%202023%2C%20set%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20inflow%20in%20three%20years.%20The%20nation%20stood%20out%20in%20August%2C%20when%20overseas%20funds%20sold%20shares%20in%20almost%20every%20other%20Asian%20emerging%20market%20amid%20a%20global%20selloff.%20Onshore%20Chinese%20stocks%20saw%20a%20record%20outflow%20last%20month%20as%20Beijing's%20attempts%20to%20restore%20market%20confidence%20fell%20flat%20with%20investors%20amid%20persistent%20worries%20over%20a%20property%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20favorite%20market%20in%20Asia%20remains%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Wood%2C%20the%20global%20head%20of%20equity%20strategy%20at%20Jefferies%20LLC%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Bloomberg%20Television%20interview%20this%20week.%20Wood%20described%20India%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmarket%20I%20want%20to%20be%20in%20Asia%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20foreseeing%20strong%20growth%20in%20corporate%20earnings%20led%20by%20a%20rejuvenating%20private%20investment%20and%20real%20estate%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20nearly%20tripled%20its%20value%20since%20the%20pandemic%20low%20for%20global%20equities%20in%20March%202020%2C%20India%20is%20now%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20stock%20market%2C%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg%20show.%20The%20US%20has%20seen%20its%20market%20capitalization%20about%20double%20in%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilan-based%20Generali%20Investments%20is%20bullish%20on%20India%20for%20its%20economic%20growth%20and%20earnings%20outlook%2C%20according%20to%20Michele%20Morganti%2C%20the%20firm's%20senior%20equity%20strategist.%20Generali%20reduced%20its%20overweight%20on%20China%20last%20month%20as%20policymakers%20opt%20for%20limited%20measures%20to%20help%20companies%20and%20boost%20sentiment%20over%20an%20all-out%20stimulus%20plan%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20there%20are%20several%20risks%20on%20the%20horizon%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResurgent%20crude%20oil%20prices%20threaten%20to%20worsen%20inflation%20dynamics%20for%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20already%20troubled%20by%20a%20surge%20in%20prices%20of%20everyday%20items%20from%20tomatoes%20to%20onions.%20Rupee%20meanwhile%20is%20hovering%20near%20a%20record%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20to%20navigate%20a%20general%20election%20in%20April-May%20that%20some%20strategists%20say%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20swing%20markets.%20In%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20market%20watchers%20will%20also%20closely%20scrutinize%20India's%20ability%20to%20build%20fast%20and%20adequate%20infrastructure%2C%20lift%20education%20standards%20and%20create%20enough%20jobs%20for%20a%20burgeoning%20young%20population%20amid%20a%20rising%20threat%20from%20the%20increased%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAperture%20Investors%20ranks%20among%20the%20holdouts%20that%20aren't%20boosting%20exposure.%20India%20needs%20years%20of%20improvements%20in%20its%20infrastructure%20and%20private-sector%20buildout%20before%20it%20can%20replace%20China%20in%20portfolios%2C%20said%20Peter%20Marber%2C%20the%20New%20York-based%20head%20of%20emerging%20markets%20at%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20financial%20investors%20are%20retreating%20from%20Chinese%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20doesn't%20lead%20to%20a%20complete%20shift%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Marber%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20aren't%20nearly%20the%20number%20of%20investable%20companies%20and%20assets%20in%20India%20versus%20in%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%20though%2C%20markets%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20positives.%20The%20NSE%20Nifty%2050%20Index%20has%20jumped%20almost%206%25%20in%20dollar%20terms%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months%2C%20beating%20the%20broader%20MSCI%20Emerging%20Markets%20Index%20by%20more%20than%207%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%