hosting%20the%20two-day-long%20G20%20Leader's%20Summit%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20at%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20starting%20today.%20The%20Summit%20would%20commence%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20world%20leaders%20at%20the%20venue%20(Bharat%20Mandapam)%20from%209%3A30%20am%20onwards.%20The%20theme%20of%20this%20year's%20G20%20Summit%2C%20which%20is%20taking%20place%20under%20India's%20presidency%20is%20%26quot%3BVasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BOne%20Earth%20-%20One%20Family%20-%20One%20Future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia's%20Crown%20Prince%20has%20travelled%20to%20India%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20statement.%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20bin%20Abdulaziz%20Al%20Saud%20is%20accompanied%20by%20a%20high-level%20delegation%2C%20including%20Ministers%20and%20senior%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2011%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20PM%20will%20call%20on%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20bin%20Salman%20bin%20Abdulaziz%20Al%20Saud%20will%20hold%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20both%20the%20leaders%20leaders%20will%20co-chair%20the%20First%20Leaders'%20Meeting%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20will%20review%20the%20progress%20made%20under%20the%20two%20Ministerial%20Committees%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Council%20i.e.%20the%20Committee%20on%20Political%2C%20Security%2C%20Social%20and%20Cultural%20Cooperation%20and%20the%20Committee%20on%20Economy%20and%20Investments%20Cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Crown%20Prince%20will%20discuss%20all%20aspects%20of%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20including%20political%2C%20security%2C%20defence%2C%20trade%20and%20economic%2C%20cultural%20and%20people-to-people%20ties.%20Both%20the%20leaders%20will%20also%20discuss%20the%20regional%20and%20international%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Crown%20Prince%20visited%20India%20on%20a%20State%20visit%20in%20February%202019%20and%20the%20current%20visit%20will%20be%20his%20second%20State%20visit%20to%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20have%20historically%20close%20and%20friendly%20relations%20with%20extensive%20people-to-people%20contacts.%20The%20trade%20between%20both%20countries%20reached%20all%20time%20high%20of%20USD%2052.75%20billion%20in%20FY%202022-23%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20second-largest%20trading%20partner%20whereas%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20India's%20fourth-largest%20trading%20partner.%20Both%20countries%20also%20have%20a%20strong%20partnership%20in%20the%20area%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20MEA%20there%20is%20a%20vibrant%20Indian%20community%20of%20around%202.4%20million%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20Their%20contribution%20towards%20the%20development%20of%20the%20host%20country%20and%20role%20as%20bridges%20to%20deepen%20the%20multifaceted%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20highly%20appreciated.%20The%20Kingdom%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20also%20facilitates%20Hajj%20pilgrimage%20of%20over%20175%2C000%20Indians%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694230200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fhljpl748_mohammed-bin-salman-and-modi_625x300_23_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaudi-arabai-crown-prince-mohammed-bin-salman-to-attend-g20-hold-bilateral-meeting-with-pm-modi-4373335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabi