3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23945744-judge-steve-jones-rules-against-mark-meadows-bid-to-move-prosecution-to-federal-court-090823%5C%22%3Eruling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20US%20District%20Court%20Judge%20Steve%20Jones%20denied%20Meadows'%20bid%20to%20move%20the%20prosecution%20against%20him%20to%20federal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20ruling%2C%20Jones%20argued%20that%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-meadows-asks-dismiss-georgia-rico-charges-doing-job-2023-8%5C%22%3EMeadows%20urged%20Georgia's%20secretary%20of%20state%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%26quot%3B%20enough%20votes%20to%20declare%20Trump%20the%20winner%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%202020%20election%2C%20his%20behavior%20fell%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20his%20official%20duties%20of%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%20and%2C%20thus%2C%20the%20prosecution%20against%20him%20should%20continue%20in%20Georgia%20state%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeadows's%20participation%20on%20the%20January%202%2C%202021%2C%20call%20was%20political%20in%20nature%20and%20involved%20the%20President's%20private%20litigation%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20are%20related%20to%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20White%20House%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20wrote%20in%20his%20ruling%2C%20which%20Meadows'%20legal%20team%20promptly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23945743-mark-meadows-appeals-judgement-ruling-against-moving-prosecution-to-federal-court-090823%5C%22%3Eappealed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Court%20finds%20that%20these%20contributions%20to%20the%20phone%20call%20with%20Secretary%20Raffensperger%20went%20beyond%20those%20activities%20that%20are%20within%20the%20official%20role%20of%20White%20House%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%20such%20as%20scheduling%20the%20President's%20phone%20calls%2C%20observing%20meetings%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20wrap%20up%20meetings%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20Presid