nent-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EBirmingham%2C%20the%20second-biggest%20city%20in%20Britain%2C%20declared%20itself%20bankrupt%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20sending%C2%A0shockwaves%20through%20the%20city's%20governance.%C2%A0The%20Labour-run%20administration%20representing%20the%20UK's%20second-largest%20city%20issued%20a%20114%20notice%2C%20putting%20a%20stop%20to%20all%20but%20essential%20spending%20and%20becoming%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20councils%20to%20plunge%20into%20financial%20distress%2C%20as%20per%20the%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2023%2Fsep%2F05%2Fcouncils-in-england-in-crisis-as-birmingham-declares-itself-bankrupt%5C%22%3E%20Guardian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Section%20114%20notice%20is%20issued%20by%20a%20council%20when%20it%20believes%20its%20income%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20spending.%C2%A0Thurrock%2C%20Croydon%2C%20Slough%2C%20and%20Northamptonshire%20have%20all%20issued%20Section%20114%20notices%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20behind%20the%20city%20going%20bankrupt%20is%20the%20equal%20pay%20claim.%C2%A0The%20City%20Council%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20pay%20760%20million%20pounds%20(%24955%20million)%20in%20equal%20pay%20claims%20it%20owes%20to%20female%20government%20employees%20who%20were%20paid%20less%20than%20men%20in%20the%20past.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20council%20revealed%20it%20had%20paid%20out%201.1%20billion%20pounds%20to%20female%20workers%20but%20still%20had%20a%20current%20liability%20of%20650-750%20million%20pounds%2C%20accruing%20at%20a%20rate%20of%205%20million%20pounds%20to%2014%20million%20pounds%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_CEBEBEA1-1EA1-CEC4-8A6E-661DF231CB30%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EThe%20city%20now%20expects%20to%20have%20a%20deficit%20of%2087%20million%20pounds%20for%20the%202023-24%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20Council%20has%20insufficient%20resources%20to%20meet%20the%20equal%20pay%20expenditure%20and%20currently%20does%20not%20have%20any%20other%20means%20of%20meeting%20this%20liability.%20The%20notice%20means%20all%20new%20spending%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20protecting%20vulnerable%20people%20and%20statutory%20services%2C%20must%20stop%20immediately%2C''%20the%20Birmingham%20City%20Council%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20bankruptcy%20was%20years%20in%20the%20making.%C2%A0As%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-birmingham-66730165%5C%22%3EBBC%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20these%20claims%20date%20back%20to%202012%2C%20when%20a%20group%20of%20170%20women%20%E2%80%93%20including%20teaching%20assistants%2C%20cleaners%2C%20and%20catering%20staff%20%E2%80%93%20won%20the%20right%20to%20proceed%20with%20equal%20pay%20claims%20against%20the%20council%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0They%20claimed%20that%20the%20council%20failed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20the%20same%20benefits%20and%20payments%20as%20men%20doing%20equivalent%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20has%20also%20blamed%20the%20expenses%20of%20a%20new%20cloud-based%20IT%20system%20by%20Oracle%20and%20years%20of%20funding%20cuts%20by%20successive%20Tory%20governments%20for%20its%20financial%20troubles%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fbirmingham-city-council-bankrupt-impact-b2406909.html%5C%22%3EIndependent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0IT%20system%20was%20supposed%20to%20cost%2019%20million%20pounds%2C%C2%A0%20but%20after%20three%20years%20of%20delays%20in%20getting%20it%20in%20place%20and%20problems%20once%20it%20was%20installed%20mean%20it%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20cost%20100%20million%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20inflation%2C%20rising%20demand%20for%20adult%20social%20care%2C%20and%20''dramatic%20reductions''%20in%20income%20from%20business%20taxes%20are%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharon%20Thompson%2C%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20council%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Feconomy%2Fbirmingham-council-bankrupt-uk-gbr-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''Local%20government%20is%20facing%20a%20perfect%20storm.%20Like%20councils%20across%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20this%20council%20faces%20unprecedented%20financial%20challenges%2C%20from%20huge%20increases%20in%20adult%20social%20care%20demand%20and%20dramatic%20reductions%20in%20business%20rates%20incomes%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20rampant%20inflation.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20already%20provided%20extra%20funding%20for%20the%20council%2C%20at%20around%2010%20percent%20of%20its%20budget%2C%20but%20''it's%20for%20locally%20elected%20councils%20to%20manage%20their%20own%20budgets%2C''%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20spokesman%20Max%20Blain%20told%20reporters%20on%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multicultural%20city%2C%20the%20largest%20in%20central%20England%2C%20hosted%20last%20year's%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20the%202026%20European%20Athletics%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20former%20adviser%20to%20Birmingham%20City%20Council%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-birmingham-66724469%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20hosting%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20was%20among%20the%20reasons%20for%20Birmingham's%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5C64D015-697D-1AAF-3E92-6B0CA055DB53%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694227980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fkb2kjaf8_birmingham-has-declared-bankruptcy_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuks-second-largest-city-bi