e%20Crimean%20coast%20when%20they%20%26quot%3Blost%20connectivity%20and%20washed%20ashore%20harmlessly%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20alleges%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20ordered%20Starlink%20engineers%20to%20turn%20off%20the%20service%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20attack%20because%20of%20his%20concern%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20would%20respond%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%20to%20a%20Ukrainian%20attack%20on%20Russian-occupied%20Crimea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-seen-with-his-secret-twins-for-the-first-time-see-pic-4368862%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20Seen%20With%20His%20'Secret'%20Twins%20For%20The%20First%20Time%2C%20See%20Pic%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1699917639043404146%5C%22%3EMr%20Musk%20has%20denied%20accusations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20turned%20off%20the%20Starlink%20network%20in%20the%20area.%20Instead%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20simply%20not%20agreed%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20activate%20it%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Crimean%20port%20city%20of%20Sevastopol.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20his%20SpaceX%20company%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bexplicitly%20complicit%20in%20a%20major%20act%20of%20war%20and%20conflict%20escalation%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Starlink%20regions%20in%20question%20were%20not%20activated.%20SpaceX%20did%20not%20deactivate%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20billionaire%20claimed%20in%20another%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20new%20biography%2C%20simply%20tiled%3Cem%3E%20'Elon%20Musk'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20officially%20releases%20on%20September%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694227920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6ue8g1i_tesla-elon-musk_6