Fbest-mechanical-keyboard%5C%22%3Ebest%20mechanical%20keyboards%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20fans%20love%20the%20tactile%20feedback%20enough%20that%20it's%20worth%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20keyboards%20work%20using%20physical%20switches%2C%20which%20feel%20and%20sound%20different%20than%20normal%20membrane%20keyboards.%20But%20not%20all%20mechanical%20keyboards%20use%20the%20same%20type%20of%20switches%2C%20which%20means%20that%20any%20two%20keyboards%20can%20feel%20completely%20different%20to%20type%20with.%20Likewise%2C%20some%20mechanical%20keyboards%20allow%20you%20to%20swap%20out%20the%20switches%20they%20come%20with%20for%20other%20types%2C%20so%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20switch%20later%20on%20to%20install.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20simple%20rundown%20on%20the%20three%20main%20types%20of%20mechanical%20keyboard%20switches%2C%20and%20how%20each%20one%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20each%20mechanical%20keyboard%20switch%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMechanical%20keyboards%20get%20their%20name%20from%20the%20mechanical%20switches%20under%20every%20key.%20Unlike%20a%20squishy%20rubber%20membrane%20keyboard%2C%20these%20spring-loaded%20switches%20have%20a%20more%20precise%20feel%20when%20pressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20switch%20is%20built%20with%20a%20few%20key%20components.%20The%20easily%20removable%20keycap%20snaps%20onto%20the%20switch%20stem.%20The%20stem's%20shape%20and%20height%20determines%20how%20far%20and%20fast%20you%20can%20press%20it%2C%20and%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20hit%20the%20%26quot%3Bactuation%20point%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20point%20where%20it%20actually%20sends%20an%20input%20to%20your%20computer.%20The%20stem%20is%20supported%20by%20a%20spring%2C%20which%20pops%20it%20back%20up%20when%20you%20let%20go.%20Some%20key%20switches%2C%20as%20we'll%20detail%2C%20have%20extras%20that%20make%20them%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5