lenge%20for%20the%20opposition%20front%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20and%20given%20that%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20trump%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20some%20of%20its%20strongest%20pocket%20boroughs%2C%20the%20alliance%20has%20rather%20passed%20the%20test%20rather%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20of%20its%20wins%20occurred%20in%20Ghosi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20sitting%20legislator%20and%20backward%20caste%20leader%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20who%20had%20been%20elected%20on%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20ticket%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20tendered%20his%20resignation.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20candidate%20and%20veteran%20leader%20Sudhakar%20Singh%20has%20defeated%20Chauhan%20by%2042%2C759%20votes%20in%20this%20important%20constituency%20in%20eastern%20UP.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20turned%20the%20contest%20into%20a%20prestige%20battle%2C%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20and%20his%20two%20deputies%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Brijesh%20Pathak%2C%20along%20with%20prominent%20ministers%2C%20canvassing%20constantly%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20by-polls.%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20BJP%20was%20being%20considered%20as%20an%20important%20gain%20for%20the%20party%2C%20as%20it%20did%20not%20have%20a%20prominent%20leader%20in%20the%20Noniya%20Chauhan%20community%20which%20is%20a%20substantial%20voting%20bloc%20in%20regions%20around%20Varanasi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SP%20candidate%20was%20fielded%20as%20a%20INDIA%20representative%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20while%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-bsp-dalit-votes-india-nda%5C%22%3Estuck%20to%20its%20policy%20of%20not%20contesting%20by-polls%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Resultantly%2C%20the%20contest%20was%20bi-polar%20and%20the%20crucial%20Dalit%20Jatav%20voters%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20traditional%20supporters%20of%20BSP%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20leaned%20towards%20the%20INDIA%20candidate.%20In%20keeping%20with%20the%20INDIA%20narrative%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20SP%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20that%20the%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20political%20formula%20%E2%80%98PDA%E2%80%99%20(standing%20for%20%3Cem%3Epichda%20dalit%20alpsankhayak%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%E2%80%98OBC%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20minorities%E2%80%99)%20alliance%20on%20ground%20will%20trump%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20future.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETeam%20INDIA%20hai%2C%20aur%20PDA%20rajneeti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second-most%20important%20victory%20for%20INDIA%20happened%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Dhupguri%20where%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20wrested%20the%20seat%20from%20the%20BJP.%20The%20victory%20is%20an%20important%20one%20for%20the%20TMC%20in%20this%20north%20Bengal%20constituency%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20stronghold%20in%20the%20state.%20Chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20get%20a%20stronger%20foothold%20in%20north%20and%20central%20Bengal%20where%20it%20is%20considered%20relatively%20weaker%20when%20compared%20to%20its%20massive%20footprint%20in%20south%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20Dhupguri%2C%20the%20party%20will%20have%20to%20rethink%20its%20strategy%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20as%20it%20now%20risks%20losing%20in%20its%20strongholds.%20However%2C%20even%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20have%20to%20iron%20out%20its%20differences%20in%20Bengal.%20Unlike%20UP%2C%20where%20INDIA%20fielded%20a%20single%20representative%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20had%20fielded%20its%20candidate%20in%20Dhupguri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Left%20candidate%20secured%20merely%2013%2C000%20votes%2C%20but%20turned%20the%20contest%20into%20a%20nail-biting%20affair%20where%20TMC%20barely%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finish%20line%2C%20edging%20past%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20by%20only%20around%204%2C000%20votes.%20The%20division%20of%20votes%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20may%20harm%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20if%20TMC-Left%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20rivalry%20is%20not%20resolved%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKerala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Kerala%2C%20former%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Oommen%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Chandy%20Oommen%20registered%20a%20comprehensive%20win%20over%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Alliance%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20in%20Puthupally%2C%20improving%20upon%20even%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20performance.%20The%20seat%20was%20vacated%20by%20the%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%E2%80%99s%20death.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NDA%20candidate%20lost%20his%20deposit.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20Bengal%2C%20the%20rivalry%20between%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20can%20in%20no%20way%20give%20an%20advantage%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20been%20a%20non-starter%20in%20the%20state%20for%20years%20now%20despite%20desperate%20efforts%20to%20make%20an%20impact.%20Whichever%20party%20wins%20in%20Kerala%2C%20it%20will%20only%20add%20to%20the%20INDIA%20tally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETripura%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20can%20derive%20some%20solace%20over%20its%20wins%20in%20two%20constituencies%20of%20Tripura.%20It%20retained%20Dhanpur%20and%20wrested%20Boxanagar%20from%20the%20CPI(M).%20The%20Boxanagar%20victory%20is%20a%20significant%20one%20for%20the%20saffron%20party%20as%20it%20was%20up%20against%20a%20combined%20opposition%20in%20the%20segment.%20The%20victory%20margin%20of%20nearly%2030%2C000%20votes%20will%20make%20the%20win%20sweeter%20for%20the%20BJP%20as%20its%20candidate%20Taffajal%20Hossain%20secured%20almost%2066%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%2C%20defeating%20CPI(M)%E2%80%99s%20Mizan%20Hossain%20who%20got%20merely%203%2C909%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Dumri%2C%20the%20ruling%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20candidate%20retained%20his%20seat%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20retained%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Bageshwar%20but%20not%20without%20a%20stiff%20challenge%20by%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20by-polls%20indicate%20that%20INDIA%20could%20pose%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20But%20before%20that%20it%20will%20need%20to%20iron%20out%20some%20of%20the%20state-level%20differences%20between%20its%20constituents%20and%20arrive%20at%20a%20mutually-agreed%20formula%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694185839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08203848%2FF5gSLmUbMAAkNUm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bypoll-ghosi-dhupguri-kerala-tripura%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20by-polls%20indicate%20that%20INDIA%20could%20pose%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20But%20before%20that%20it%20will%20need%20to%20iron%20out%20some%20of%20the%20state-level%20differences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bypoll-ghos