n%20early%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20children%20begging%20at%20traffic%20lights%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20leave.%20At%20least%2025%20slums%20have%20been%20demolished%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20residents%20evacuated%2C%20with%20no%20alternative%20accommodation.%20They%20have%20lost%20their%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20French%20national%20daily%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2023%2F09%2F07%2Fin-india-modi-makes-new-delhi-s-poverty-temporarily-disappear-for-the-g20-summit_6128001_4.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwhat-the-world-is-reading-around-indias-g20-presidency%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20World%20is%20Reading%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20poor%20are%20being%20removed%20from%20sight%20ahead%20of%20an%20important%20international%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Indu%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20that%20monitors%20homeless%20shelters%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20told%20the%20Boston-based%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csmonitor.com%2FWorld%2FAsia-South-Central%2F2023%2F0907%2FG20-face-lift-Delhi-removes-poor-people-but-not-poverty%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChristian%20Science%20Monitor%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E(CSM)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20tries%20its%20best%20to%20hide%20its%20poverty%2C%20stripping%20the%20disadvantaged%20of%20dignity.%20They%20consider%20them%20an%20eyesore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Information%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20was%20quoted%20by%20US-based%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2023%2F09%2F06%2Findia-new-delhi-g20-summit-modi-china-russia-ukraine%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eforeignpolicy.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Esaying%20that%20the%20country%20has%20hosted%20more%20than%20200%20meetings%20in%20more%20than%2060%20cities%20since%20taking%20the%20mantle%20from%20Indonesia%20last%20year.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20also%20aims%20to%20leverage%20its%20growing%20global%20footprint%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20wealthy%20economies%20and%20the%20global%20south%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20all%20while%20rampaging%20over%20its%20own%20people%2C%20apparently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20visit%20in%202020%20was%20marked%20by%20similar%20hurried%20attempts%20to%20hide%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20poor%20behind%20curtains%20of%20blue%20and%20green%20tarpaulin%2C%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20preparations%20for%20G20.%20But%20this%20time%20the%20authorities%20did%20not%20stop%20at%20raising%20walls%2C%20thousands%20of%20houses%20were%20razed%20and%20entire%20slums%20uprooted%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20outskirts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20New%20Delhi%20busied%20itself%20in%20hiding%20the%20poor%2C%20in%20what%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20contradictory%20move%2C%20it%20also%20created%20a%20whole%20new%20population%20of%20homeless%20people%20through%20these%20demolition%20drives%2C%20CSM%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAd%20here%20Ad%20there%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20strategic%20beatification%20attempts%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbillboards%20and%20bus%20stops%20in%20every%20Indian%20city%20are%20plastered%20with%20images%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Japanese%20newspaper%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FOpinion%2FIndia-s-Modi-is-not-the-world-s-guru%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENikkei%20Asia%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Epointed%20out.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20never%20seen%20an%20advertising%20blitz%20of%20this%20magnitude.%20A%20former%20finance%20secretary%20estimated%20the%20cost%20at%20Rs%2010%20billion%20(%24121%20million)%20and%20rising%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20for%20the%20visiting%20dignitaries%3F%20Surely%2C%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCritics%20who%20think%20Modi%20is%20trying%20to%20impress%20foreign%20visitors%20are%20clearly%20mistaken.%20This%20advertising%20blitz%20is%20aimed%20at%20financing%20the%20promotion%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20the%20election%20run-up%2C%20portraying%20him%20as%20a%20great%20leader%20of%20not%20just%20India%20but%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Japanese%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20of%20course%20convenient%20to%20have%20the%20government%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20pay%20for%20this%20ad%20campaign.%20Indian%20politicians%20of%20all%20stripes%20have%20done%20similar%20things%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20current%20campaign%20beggars%20description%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-g20-under-indian-presidency-achievements-challenges-and-unmet-expectations%5C%22%3EThe%20G20%20Under%20Indian%20Presidency%3A%20Achievements%2C%20Challenges%2C%20and%20Unmet%20Expectations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20report%20by%20the%20CNBC%E2%80%99s%20Martin%20Soong%2C%20standing%20a%20few%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20India%20Gate%2C%20said%20that%20the%20summit%20%E2%80%9Cthreatens%20to%20be%20overshadowed%20by%20Modi%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20talking%20about%20the%20criticism%20he%20has%20drawn%20for%20using%20the%20event%20as%20almost%20a%20way%20to%20start%20campaigning%20for%20the%20elections%20next%20year.%20And%20he%E2%80%99s%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20made%20a%20real%20spectacle%20of%20the%20G20%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soong%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%E2%80%99s%20a%20train-ride%20of%20meetings%20that%20culminate%20in%20the%20summit%20and%20they%E2%80%99ve%20%5BIndia%5D%20has%20had%20200%20%5Bof%20those%5D..we%E2%80%99ve%20never%20seen%20that%20kind%20of%20number%20of%20meetings%20before%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20any%20G20%20summit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFirst%20G20%20summit%20that%20may%20fail%20to%20produce%20a%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fasia%2F2023%2F09%2F07%2Fthe-g20-summit-will-be-a-resounding-success-for-india%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Economist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20questioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20what%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20to%20show%20for%20all%20the%20PR%20buzz.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20smiling%20face%20has%20beamed%20down%20from%20these%20ads.%20What%20does%20he%20have%20to%20show%20for%20it%3F%20High-level%20G20%20meetings%20over%20the%20past%20year%20have%20repeatedly%20failed%20to%20reach%20consensus.%20Summits%20of%20ministers%20on%20anything%20from%20finance%20to%20climate%20change%20ended%20without%20the%20customary%20joint%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20they%20settled%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98outcome%20document%E2%80%99%20that%20notes%20areas%20of%20agreement%20as%20well%20as%20discord%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20wording%20around%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20that%20the%20summit%20of%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20over%20the%20weekend%20will%20achieve%20what%20no%20ministerial%20grouping%20has%20done%20so%20far.%20That%20would%20make%20it%20the%20first%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit%20to%20fail%20to%20issue%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20UK-based%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694177238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08181353%2FLead-image-size.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fremoving-poverty-not-the-poor-will-make-delhi-beautiful-global-opinion-on-indias-g20-pr-blitz%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20the%20strategic%20beautification%20drive%2C%20New%20Delhi%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20an%20advertising%20storm.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fremoving-poverty-not-the-poor-will-make-delhi-beautiful-global-opinion-on-indias-g20-pr-blitz%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Reliance%2C%20Tata%20Group%20set%20to%20announce%20AI%20partnership%20with%20Nvidia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694177098000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1679903084-5252.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fafter-reliance-tata-group-set-to-announce-ai-partnership-with-nvidia-123090800869_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20will%20create%20AI%20applications%20and%20services%20for%20their%20450%20million%20Jio%20customers%20and%20provide%20AI%20infrastructure%20to%20scientists%2C%20developers%20and%20startups%20across%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fafter-reliance-tata-group-set-to-announce-ai-partne