timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-condemns-fake-elections-in-russian-occupied-areas%2Famp_articleshow%2F103510927.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-condemns-fake-elections-in-russian-occupied-areas%2Famp_articleshow%2F103510927.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20Is%20INDIA-1%20and%20NDA-0%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%E2%80%99s%20INDIA%201%2C%20NDA%200%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20using%20all%20its%20might%20and%20resources%2C%20deploying%20Hindutva%20as%20well%20as%20caste%20calculations%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20lost%20the%20Ghosi%20assembly%20by-poll%20election%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20winning.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20particular%2C%20but%20a%20source%20of%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20straight%20contest%20between%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20NDA.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20field%20a%20nominee%20but%20supported%20the%20SP%20candidate.%20The%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20did%20not%20contest%20the%20by-poll%2C%20maintaining%20its%20position%20of%20officially%20staying%20away%20from%20both%20NDA%20and%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGhosi%20did%20not%20make%20victorious%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20SP%20but%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20and%20this%20is%20also%20going%20to%20be%20the%20result%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20in%20a%20congratulatory%20note%20for%20voters%20of%20Ghosi.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20victory%20of%20positive%20politics%20and%20the%20defeat%20of%20communal%2C%20negative%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20result%20reflected%20the%20success%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20new%20formula%20against%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ETeam%20INDIA%20hai%2C%20aur%20PDA%20(Pichda%20Dalit%20Alpsankhyak)%20rajneeti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%E2%80%99s%20veteran%20leader%20Sudhakar%20Singh%2C%20a%20two-time%20former%20MLA%2C%20has%20defeated%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20of%20the%20BJP%20by%2042%2C759%20votes%20in%20Ghosi.%20According%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20after%2033%20rounds%2C%20Singh%20secured%201.24%20lakh%20votes%2C%2057.19%25%2C%20while%20Chauhan%20got%2081%2C668%20votes%20(37.54%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20and%20his%20deputies%20Maurya%20and%20Pathak%20are%20yet%20to%20react%20to%20the%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20deputed%20its%20state%20president%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20Chaudhary%20to%20face%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20political%20point%20of%20view%20the%20result%20was%20not%20one%20we%20expected%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Chaudhary.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20asked%20if%20the%20opposition%20would%20still%20question%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%20and%20government%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20the%20opposition%20question%20the%20EVMs%20after%20this%20result%3F%20Will%20they%20question%20government%20machinery%2C%20constitutional%20institutions%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20by-polls%20mattered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20by-poll%20was%20held%20after%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20sitting%20SP%20MLA%2C%20resigned%20from%20his%20seat%20and%20party%20in%20July%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20OBC%20leaders%20Chauhan%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20to%20its%20fold%20after%20a%20short%20stint%20with%20the%20SP%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20received%20a%20huge%20boost%20as%20it%20prepared%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20However%2C%20the%20defeat%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20where%20not%20just%20Rajbhar%20but%20over%20a%20dozen%20ministers%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20cabinet%20including%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%20extensively%20campaigned%20for%20Chauhan%2C%20has%20put%20the%20BJP%20in%20an%20awkward%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20also%20played%20the%20Hindutva%20card%20openly%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20by-poll%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Mau%20district%20of%20Purvanchal%2C%20abutting%20Azamgarh.%20Addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Ghosi%20on%20September%202%2C%20Adityanath%20reminded%20voters%20of%20the%20firing%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekarsevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20Ayodhya%20ordered%20by%20the%20then%20Mulayam%20Singh%20government%20in%201990.%20Adityanath%20also%20linked%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20to%20the%202005%20Mau%20communal%20violence.%20SP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20is%20important%20would%20be%20understood%20by%20those%20who%20closely%20felt%20the%202005%20riots%20in%20Mau.%20Under%20the%20then%20SP%20government%2C%20rioters%20and%20mafia%2C%20brandishing%20weapons%20openly%2C%20were%20killing%20Yadavs%20in%20some%20places%20and%20Dalits%20in%20others.%20The%20Congress%20government%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre%20then%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20and%20the%20SP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20could%20not%20do%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adityanath.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20reminded%20voters%20how%20he%20reached%20Mau%20from%20Gorakhpur%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20MP%20of%20Gorakhpur%20then.%20And%20to%20fight%20these%20rioters%2C%20I%20came%20down%20from%20Gorakhpur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20generating%20loud%20applause%20from%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Adityanath%20did%20not%20name%20jailed%C2%A0%20former%20MLA%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%2C%20who%20has%20faced%20the%20biggest%20brunt%20of%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20made%20an%20unmistakable%20reference%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mafia%20who%20were%20earlier%20brandishing%20weapons%2C%20today%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20a%20wheelchair%20begging%20for%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Ansari%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20instigating%20the%20Mau%20riots.%20His%20son%20Abbas%20Ansari%20had%20stood%20second%20in%20Ghosi%20in%202017%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20by%20a%20thin%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudhakar%20Singh%2C%20who%20won%20from%20Ghosi%20in%201996%20and%202012%2C%20had%20stood%20third%20in%202017.%20A%20Kshatriya%20by%20caste%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20defeat%20Chauhan%20in%20this%20by-poll%20despite%20heavy%20mobilisation%20of%20caste%20leaders%20in%20particular%20OBCs%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20served%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20from%202017%20to%202022%20before%20resigning%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20and%20joining%20the%20SP.%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20had%20served%20as%20minister%20for%20forest%2C%20environment%20and%20zoological%20gardens%2C%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter%20had%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20tampering%20with%20reservations%20for%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20and%20neglecting%20their%20interests%20despite%20coming%20to%20power%20through%20their%20support.%20Chauhan%20belongs%20to%20the%20Noniya%20Chauhan%20backward%20caste.%20Traditionally%20engaged%20in%20salt%20trading%2C%20the%20community%20is%20also%20known%20by%20other%20names%20such%20as%20Loniya-Chauhan%20and%20Gole-Thakur%2C%20and%20consider%20Prithviraj%20Chauhan%20among%20their%20icons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20scattered%20in%20parts%20of%20east%20UP%20but%20are%20an%20important%20vote%20bloc%20in%20rural%20areas%20adjoining%20Varanasi%2C%20Azamgarh%2C%20Chandauli%20and%20Mau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20twice%20as%20an%20SP%20candidate%2C%20in%201996%20and%202000.%20When%20Mayawati%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20in%202007%2C%20he%20shifted%20loyalties%20and%20in%202009%20won%20his%20first%20and%20only%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Ghosi%20on%20a%20BSP%20symbol.%20He%20was%20also%20appointed%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20BSP%20parliamentary%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20seat%20to%20the%20BJP.%20And%20a%20year%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Chauhan%20joined%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20contested%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20Madhuban%20seat%20in%20the%202017%20assembly%20election.%20He%20won%20and%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%20In%202022%2C%20after%20rebelling%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20won%20from%20Ghosi%20on%20an%20SP%20ticket.%20However%2C%20he%20soon%20started%20distancing%20himself%20from%20the%20Opposition%20party%20and%20in%20July%20formally%20resigned%20as%20an%20MLA%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defeat%20in%20Ghosi%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20who%20had%20just%20recently%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20actively%20campaigned%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20which%20has%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20voters%20of%20the%20Rajbhar%20community%2C%20an%20OBC%20caste.%20By%20ensuring%20a%20BJP%20win%2C%20he%20could%20have%20demonstrated%20his%20indispensability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20this%20election%20also%20marked%20the%20return%20to%20active%20campaigning%20of%20Akhilesh%20%E2%80%98s%20uncle%20Shivpal%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20held%20several%20public%20meetings%20in%20the%20by-poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20All-India%20Chauhan%20Federation%2C%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20July%20assumed%20significance%20as%20the%20party%20lacked%20a%20popular%20face%20from%20the%20community%20after%20six-time%20MLA%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20Bihar%20in%202019.%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20is%20the%20current%20governor%20of%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20rebellions%20by%20OBC%20leaders%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20others%20had%20caused%20heavy%20losses%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202022%2C%20the%20party%20was%20desperate%20to%20set%20its%20caste%20arithmetic%20right%20as%20it%20approached%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20sees%20Purvanchal%20as%20a%20problem%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20won%20273%20seats%20in%20the%20403-member%20assembly%20in%202022%2C%20it%20fared%20poorly%20in%20southern%20and%20central%20parts%20of%20east%20UP.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20SP%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20125%20seats%20came%20from%20these%20backward%20regions.%20The%20BJP%20lost%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Ghazipur%2C%20three%20out%20of%20four%20in%20Mau%2C%20five%20out%20of%20nine%20in%20Jaunpur%2C%20five%20out%20of%20seven%20in%20Ballia%2C%20all%20ten%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20four%20out%20of%20five%20in%20Basti%2C%20all%20five%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20three%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Barabanki%2C%20all%20three%20in%20Kaushambi%20and%20five%20out%20of%20seven%20in%20Pratapgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%2C%20several%20BJP%20ministers%2C%20including%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Brijesh%20Pathak%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20allies%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20Ashish%20Patel%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20campaigned%20heavily%20for%20Chauhan.%20The%20party%20deployed%20minister%20Danish%20Azad%2C%20its%20Muslim%20face%2C%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Muslim%20voters%20in%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20had%20even%20accused%20the%20local%20police%20and%20administration%20of%20working%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20trying%20to%20pressure%20people%20in%20Muslim%20areas%20against%20voting%20for%20it%20and%20harassing%20its%20workers.%20The%20party%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20chief%20election%20officer%20of%20UP%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20influence%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20as%20Sudhakar%20Singh%20started%20building%20his%20lead%20over%20Chauhan%2C%20Nishad%20Party%20chief%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20under%20Adityanath%2C%20equated%20areas%20with%20a%20Muslim%20population%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20insinuated%20that%20the%20SP%20was%20ahead%20as%20only%20votes%20of%20Muslim%20areas%20had%20been%20counted%20till%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20boxes%20(EVMs)%20in%20Pakistan%20areas%20are%20counted%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20Pakistan%20is%20winning.%20But%20when%20the%20boxes%20in%20our%20areas%20come%20out%2C%20they%20(Pakistan)%20go%20out%20of%20the%20picture%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy-polls%20don%E2%80%99t%20generally%20reflect%20the%20larger%20mood%20of%20the%20people%20and%20it%20has%20been%20established%20in%20the%20last%20few%20elections%20that%20voters%20think%20differently%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20national%20elections.%20In%202018%20too%2C%20the%20SP-led%20alliance%20won%20three%20crucial%20Lok%20Sabha%20by-poll%20elections%20in%20UP%20%E2%80%93%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Kairana%20and%20Phulpur%20%E2%80%93%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%202019%20election%20result%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20different.%20However%2C%20under%20the%20ever-changing%20political%20situation%20and%20high%20charged%20campaign%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20dismiss%20the%20prospects%20of%20INDIA%2C%20the%20Ghosi%20win%20is%20a%20big%20boost%20to%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20and%20their%20workers%20as%20they%20prepare%20to%20take%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Adityanath%20and%20co%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20campaigning%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20Akhilesh%20had%20said%20the%20by-poll%20was%20not%20an%20ordinary%20assembly%20election%20but%20a%20message%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20After%20the%20win%2C%20Akhilesh%20said%20UP%20would%20once%20again%20lead%20the%20charge%20for%20change%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20report%20was%20edited%20since%20publication%20with%20the%20final%20tally%20of%20the%20bypoll%20results.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694174665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victory%20in%20the%20Ghosi%20assembly%20seat%20is%20not%20only%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20particular%2C%20but%20a%20source%20of%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Lee%20rapidly%20strengthens%20to%20'life-threatening'%20Category%205%20storm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694173500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-hurricane-lee-caribbean_6277346.jpg%3F20230907132548%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhurricane-lee-rapidly-strengthens-to-category-5-storm-which-could-bring-life-threatening-conditions-12957348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Lee%20has%20strengthened%20into%20a%20major%20Category%205%20storm%2C%20with%20the%20National%20Hurricane%20Center%20issuing%20a%20warning%20for%20%26quot%3Blife-threatening%26quot%3B%20surf%20and%20rip%20conditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhurricane-lee-rapidly-strengthens-to-category-5-storm-which-could-bring-life-threatening-conditions-12957348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhurricane-lee-rapidly-strengthens-to-category-5-storm-which-could-bring-life-threatening-conditions-12957348%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhurricane-lee-rapidly-strengthens-to-category-5-storm-which-could-bring-life-threatening-conditions-12957348%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Ukraine%20war%20intervention%20could%20be%20worrying%20sign%20of%20things%20to%20come%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694173200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-elon-musk-twitter_6278310.jpg%3F20230908130220%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musk-ukraine-starlink-intervention-could-be-worrying-sign-of-things-to-come-12957345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20intervention%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20will%20be%20deeply%20troubling%20to%20many%20but%20it%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20things%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musk-ukraine-starlink-intervention-could-be-worrying-sign-of-things-to-come-12957345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musk-ukraine-starlink-intervention-could-be-worrying-sign-of-things-to-come-12957345%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musk-ukraine-starlink-intervention-could-be-worrying-sign-of-things-to-come-12957345%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vishwaguru%20and%20the%20Crisis%20of%20Democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20August%20survey%20by%20the%20reputed%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpew-research-finds-indians-more-confident-of-country-than-rest-of-world%5C%22%3E68%25%20of%20Indians%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20influence%20has%20gotten%20stronger.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flokniti.org%2Fmedia%2Fupload_files%2FSocial-and-Political-Barometer-2023-Survey-findings.pdf%5C%22%3E2023%20Lokniti-CSDS%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2054%25%20(and%2071%25%20of%20those%20with%20high%20media%20exposure)%20believed%20that%20India%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20Vishwaguru%C2%A0under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Narendra%20Modi.%20According%20to%20Pew%2C%2079%25%20of%20Indians%20have%20a%20favourable%20view%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20surveys%20do%20not%20tell%20us%20the%20complete%20reality%2C%20but%20are%20an%20important%20statistical%20tool%20to%20understand%20large%20social%20trends.%20Why%20are%20these%20facts%2C%20therefore%2C%20noteworthy%3F%20Because%20they%20do%20not%20match%20with%20foreign%20assessments%20about%20the%20world%20standing%20of%20India%2C%20or%20that%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20according%20to%20Pew%2C%20only%20a%2028%25%20median%20(19%20countries)%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20influence%20has%20grown%20stronger.%20While%20a%2046%25%20median%20(23%20countries)%20had%20a%20favourable%20opinion%20of%20India%20(against%2034%25%20unfavourability%20rating)%2C%20in%20many%20of%20these%20countries%2C%20especially%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20favourability%20of%20India%20was%20substantially%20higher%20in%20earlier%20surveys%20in%202008%2F2013.%20And%2C%20unlike%20domestic%20opinion%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20propagation%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20Modi%20is%20a%20popular%20global%20leader%20leading%20the%20world%2C%20only%2037%25%20median%20in%2012%20countries%20have%20confidence%20in%20him%20against%2040%25%20who%20have%20no%20confidence.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20where%2051%25%20people%20favour%20India%2C%20the%20confidence%20in%20Modi%20is%2021%25%2C%20while%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%2071%25%20favours%20India%2C%20the%20confidence%20in%20him%20is%2041%25%20demonstrating%20huge%20gaps.%20As%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20Americans%20(and%2059%25%20in%20the%2018-29%20age%20category)%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20Modi%20(the%20lowest%20percentage%20amongst%20the%20leaders%20in%20the%20survey%3A%20Zelenskyy%2C%20Macron%2C%20Scholz%2C%20Netanyahu%2C%20Modi%2C%20Xi%20and%20Putin).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20staggering%20difference%20between%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20evaluation%2C%20and%20the%20substantial%20domestic%20acceptance%2C%20even%20across%20partisan%20lines%2C%20of%20the%20belief%20that%20India%20is%20already%20a%20Vishwaguru%2C%20are%20significant%20for%20two%20things%3A%20first%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20government%20in%20making%20their%20version%20of%20nationalism%20almost%20ironclad%2C%20and%20second%2C%20the%20relevance%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20post-truth.%20Post-truth%2C%20as%20scholars%20describe%20it%2C%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cerosion%20of%20simple%20factual%20truths%2C%20truths%20that%20technically%20anyone%20could%20verify%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20systematic%20use%20of%20blatant%20lies%E2%80%9D.%20While%20lies%20always%20existed%20in%20history%2C%20under%20post-truth%2C%20truth%20itself%20becomes%20immaterial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Will%20India's%20'Development'%20Move%20Past%20Bombast%20and%20Pretending%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-indias-development-move-past-bombast-and-pretending%5C%22%3EWill%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Development%E2%80%99%20Move%20Past%20Bombast%20and%20Pretending%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20while%20the%20official%20discourse%20is%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20has%20increased%20phenomenally%20under%20Modi%2C%20and%20the%20tagline%20for%20G20%20is%20India%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9CMother%20of%20Democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20Kafkaesque%20irony%2C%20India%20has%20suffered%20the%20greatest%20loss%20of%20global%20reputation%20since%20the%20Emergency%20of%201975%20precisely%20because%20of%20severe%20democracy%20erosion%20and%20religious%20majoritarianism%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20This%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20widespread%2C%20global%20condemnation%20and%20criticism%2C%20as%20documented%20by%20the%20responses%20from%20foreign%20media%20and%20academia%2C%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20reports%20and%20rankings%20by%20organisations%20like%20the%20Varieties%20of%20Democracy%20Institute%2C%20Freedom%20House%2C%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%2C%20Amnesty%20International%2C%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20Reporters%20without%20Borders%2C%20to%20name%20only%20a%20few%2C%20and%20even%20responses%20from%20governments%20and%20legislatures%20in%20the%20West%2C%20and%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20etc.%2C%20who%20otherwise%20practice%20only%20realpolitik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20under%20post-truth%2C%20this%20%E2%80%9Creality%E2%80%9D%20of%20criticisms%20does%20not%20make%20any%20difference%20to%20the%20domestic%20self-assessment%20of%20India%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%2C%20or%20ironically%2C%20even%20strengthens%20it.%20While%20the%20government%20and%20its%20supporters%20have%2C%20rightly%2C%20questioned%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccolonialist%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cimperialist%E2%80%9D%20Western%20governments%20in%20criticising%20the%20democracy%20record%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20they%20have%20also%2C%20wrongly%2C%20painted%20all%20foreign%20criticisms%20as%20a%20part%20of%20grand%20conspiracy%20against%20a%20rising%20India%2C%20and%20Hindu%20civilisation.%20Here%2C%20the%20domination%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20nationalism%20draws%20in%20even%20those%20who%20are%20not%20narrowly%20identified%20with%20Hindutva.%20Like%20many%20other%20majoritarian%20ethnic%20projects%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20populist%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20project%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20and%20have%20managed%20to%20build%20an%20immunity%20which%20disqualifies%20even%20domestic%20critics%20as%20anti-national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20foreign%20governments%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20West%2C%20have%20lent%20credence%20to%20the%20Vishwaguru%20narrative%20by%20increasing%20strategic%20and%20economic%20cooperation%20with%20India%20and%20with%20acts%20like%20their%20leaders%20appearing%20together%20with%20Modi%20in%20Indian%20diaspora%20rallies%2C%20duly%20marketed%20breathlessly%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%20for%20a%20domestic%20audience.%20But%20the%20fundamental%20animator%20of%20the%20changed%20geopolitical%20scenario%20in%20which%20India%20becomes%20more%20important%20is%20China%20and%20the%20necessity%20for%20a%20bulwark%20against%20it%20(in%20contrast%20to%20India%2C%20in%202019%2C%20a%20median%20of%2070%25%20in%2025%20countries%20said%20China%20played%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20the%20world%20compared%20to%20a%20decade%20before%20%E2%80%93%20Pew%202019).%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20factors%20like%20the%20demographic%20size%20of%20India%2C%20its%20inevitable%20economic%20rise%2C%20its%20democratic%20legacy%2C%20and%20the%20power%20of%20a%20large%20diaspora%2C%20which%20make%20the%20world%20increasingly%20engage%20with%20India%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20(as%20early%20as%202010%2C%20President%20Obama%20had%20said%20that%20India%20is%20not%20emerging%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Chas%20already%20risen%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20power).%20Yet%2C%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20project%20has%20successfully%20made%20these%20factors%20seem%20like%20Modi%20government%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20after%20India%20which%20has%20the%20most%20inflated%20opinion%20about%20its%20power%20is%20Russia%2C%20with%20a%2030%25%20difference%20between%20self-evaluation%20and%20foreign%20assessment%20(Pew%202018).%20And%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20kind%20of%20depredations%20its%20great%20power%20ambitions%20have%20wrought%20on%20its%20own%20people%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'They%20Really%20Descend%20on%20Journalism%20They%20Don't%20Like'%3A%20Press%20Freedom%20in%20India%2C%20on%20the%20Eve%20of%20the%20G20%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-india-press-freedom-g20-impunity-it-cell%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98They%20Really%20Descend%20on%20Journalism%20They%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Like%E2%80%99%3A%20Press%20Freedom%20in%20India%2C%20on%20the%20Eve%20of%20the%20G20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20a%20political%20discourse%20centred%20around%20Vishwaguru%20is%20deeply%20scarring%20for%20democracy.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20hide%20the%20democratic%20backsliding%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20but%20also%20deflects%20attention%20from%20the%20fundamental%20problems%20in%20a%20country%20with%20a%20nominal%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%242%2C388%20(ranked%20139%20out%20of%20192%20countries)%20and%20the%20largest%20global%20population%20of%20poor%20(230%20million%20people%2C%20almost%20equivalent%20to%20the%20fifth%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20world).%20While%2060%25%20surveyed%20in%202023%20believe%20that%20their%20incomes%20do%20not%20meet%20basic%20needs%2C%2042%25%20feel%20that%20nothing%20has%20changed%20and%2022%25%20feel%20that%20conditions%20have%20deteriorated%2C%20astonishingly%2C%2047%25%20of%20poor%20believe%20that%20India%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%20(Lokniti-CSDS%202023)%20demonstrating%20how%20post-truth%20communications%20have%20penetrated%20even%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20propaganda%2C%20fake%20news%20and%20a%20near%20domination%20of%20the%20mainstream%20media%20have%20aided%20Hindu%20nationalism%20and%20its%20Vishwaguru%20claims%20(for%20example%3A%20the%20government%20assertions%20on%20COVID-19%20vaccination%20and%20the%20Russo-Ukraine%20War).%20But%20post-truth%20in%20general%2C%20or%20specifically%20regarding%20Vishwaguru%2C%20which%20is%20also%20based%20on%20religious%20and%20civilisational%20supremacy%2C%20cannot%20be%20countered%20by%20facts%20alone.%20Facts%20cannot%20survive%20without%20socio-political%20structures%20supporting%20them.%20What%20has%20led%20to%20the%20domination%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20is%20the%20collapse%20of%20trust%20in%20%E2%80%9Csecularist%E2%80%9D%20politics%2C%20making%20the%20former%E2%80%99s%20claims%20less%20about%20facts%20and%20the%20truth%2C%20and%20more%20about%20who%20is%20making%20the%20claim.%20While%20Hindutva%20has%20been%20defeated%20electorally%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20a%20political%20imagination%20that%20can%20challenge%20its%20nationalist%20project%20and%20propose%20a%20new%2C%20inclusive%20and%20modest%20nationalism%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20identified.%20Remember%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20used%20the%20shield%20of%20a%20muscular%20nationalism%20to%20easily%20weather%20crises%20like%20demonetisation%2C%20COVID-19%20excess%20deaths%2C%20Chinese%20aggression%20at%20the%20border%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20alleged%20Adani%20stock%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20can%20be%20attempted%20in%20the%20meantime%20is%20the%20delineation%20of%20the%20ill%20effects%20on%20democracy%20of%20a%20lower%20middle-income%20country%2C%20with%20a%20human%20development%20rank%20of%20132%2C%20in%20the%20thralldom%20of%20being%20a%20Vishwaguru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENissim%20Mannathukkaren%20is%20Professor%2C%20International%20Development%20Studies%2C%20Dalhousie%20University%2C%20Canada.%20He%20tweets%20%40nmannathukkaren.%20Some%20of%20the%20arguments%20here%20and%20supporting%20data%20are%20elaborated%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1080%2F01436597.2023.2231890%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20co-authored%20with%20Drew%20MacEachern%20recently%20in%20the%20Third%20World%20Quarterly%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694172487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvishwaguru-and-the-crisis-of-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20political%20discourse%20centred%20around%20Vishwaguru%20is%20deeply%20scarring%20for%20democracy.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20hide%20the%20democratic%20backsliding%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20but%20also%20deflects%20attention%20from%20the%20fundamental%20problems%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvishwaguru-and-the-crisis-of-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Summit%20will%20chart%20new%20path%20in%20human-centric%20development%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694171866000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F28%2Ffull%2F1693241035-9035.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-will-chart-new-path-in-human-centric-development-pm-modi-123090800812_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Invoking%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%20on%20X%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20emulate%20his%20mission%20of%20serving%20the%20underprivileged%2C%20the%20very%20last%20person%20in%20the%20queue%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-