%20manuscripts%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20governments%20in%20London%20and%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20international%20trace%20of%20manuscripts%20has%20been%20a%20less%20glamorous%2C%20if%20not%20entirely%20neglected%2C%20dimension%20of%20the%20discourse%20on%20colonial%20loot%20and%20repatriation.%20There%20are%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20complexities%20involved%20in%20identifying%2C%20tracing%20and%20restituting%20manuscripts%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20as%20linguistically%20diverse%20as%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20repatriation%20of%20manuscripts%20is%20entangled%20in%20international%20diplomacy%2C%20domestic%20policies%20have%20continued%20framing%20manuscripts%20in%20terms%20of%20Sanskritic%20literacy%20and%20expertise%20that%20defy%20the%20distinctive%20history%20of%20manuscript%20traditions%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20what%20most%20people%20believe%2C%20Indian%20manuscript%20diversity%20did%20not%20rely%20only%20on%20the%20privileged%20and%20the%20educated%20for%20the%20propagation%20of%20various%20scribal%20practices.%20Recent%20research%20has%20shown%20that%20even%20as%20religious%20and%20state%20institutions%20heavily%20mandated%20scribal%20constituencies%2C%20a%20robust%20and%20eclectic%20secular%20scribal%20heritage%20emerged%20in%20the%20subcontinent.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20only%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20an%20Indological%20view%20of%20manuscripts%20that%20a%20specific%20form%20of%20religious%20literacy%20came%20to%20be%20privileged%20and%20manuscripts%20came%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20rarefied%20representatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20%E2%80%98orientalisation%E2%80%99%20of%20Indian%20manuscripts%20paralleled%20the%20colonial%20rule%20in%20India%2C%20but%20also%20exceeds%20it%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20current%20approach%20to%20manuscripts%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20remains%20driven%20by%20an%20assortment%20of%20Indological%20perspectives%20that%20privilege%20Sanskrit%20and%20Brahmanical%20texts%20over%20myriad%20traditions%20and%20functions%20of%20manuscripts%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fdebate-dont-accuse-critics-of-indology-of-being-handmaidens-of-hindutva%5C%22%3EDebate%3A%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Accuse%20Critics%20of%20Indology%20of%20Being%20Handmaidens%20of%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%2070%25%20of%20manuscripts%20under%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.namami.gov.in%2Fscripts-and-languages%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Mission%20for%20Manuscripts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20in%20Sanskrit.%20While%20the%20Sanskrit%20Indological%20manuscript%20tradition%20merits%20a%20separate%20treatment%2C%20the%20Manuscript%20Mission%20requires%20to%20also%20go%20beyond%20the%20oriental%20mindset%20and%20include%20a%20plethora%20of%20manuscripts%20that%20do%20not%20follow%20the%20Indological%20focus%20on%20Brahmanical%20antiquity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20it%20is%20salutary%20to%20consider%20examples%20from%20our%20own%20history%20where%20people%20went%20beyond%20the%20state%20mandate%20and%20identified%20and%20constructed%20a%20manuscript%20heritage%20that%20was%20reflective%20of%20a%20dynamic%20and%20inclusive%20perspective%20of%20manuscripts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20people%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20phenomenal%20contributions%20of%20Rahul%20Sankrityayan%20in%20restituting%20the%20connections%20between%20Tibetan%20and%20Bihari%20Buddhist%20philosophies.%20Sankrityayan%2C%20who%20visited%20one%20of%20the%20most%20remote%20monasteries%20in%20Tibet%20(called%20Sakya)%2C%20recovered%20Buddhist%20philosophers%20such%20as%20Dh