wenty-three%20years%2C%20with%20six%20more%20suspects%20on%20trial%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20months%20earlier%2C%20the%20new%20police%20commissioner%2C%20Mohamed%20Hameed%2C%20had%20revealed%20that%20the%20police%20knew%20of%20at%20least%201%2C400%20extremists%20in%20the%20country%20who%20%E2%80%98would%20not%20hesitate%20to%20take%20the%20life%20of%20the%20person%20next%20to%20them%E2%80%99.%20He%20reported%20that%20173%20Maldivians%20had%20crossed%20into%20Syria%2C%20with%20almost%20sixty%20in%20the%20country%20at%20that%20time.%20In%20an%20alarming%20first%2C%20three%20tourists%20were%20stabbed%20(none%20fatally)%20in%20an%20attack%20in%20Hulhumal%C3%A9%20in%20early%202020%2C%20which%20was%20also%20claimed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20State.%20The%20government%20has%20thwarted%20a%20number%20of%20further%20attacks%20and%20arrested%20Mohamed%20Ameen%2C%20an%20Islamic%20State%20recruiter%2C%20who%20was%20also%20being%20pursued%20by%20US%20authorities.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20the%20US%20treasury%20also%20placed%20sanctions%20on%20twenty%20Maldivians%20it%20considered%20to%20be%20al-Qaeda%20or%20ISIS%20operatives%2C%20including%20Aalif%20Rauf%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20and%20his%20brothers%20used%20Kuda%20Henveiru%20for%20fundraising%20and%20recruitment.%20Concerns%20persist%2C%20however%2C%20over%20the%20apparent%20inability%20to%20root%20out%20these%20malicious%20networks.%20Their%20political%20influence%20was%20demonstrated%20when%20the%20Maldivian%20Democracy%20Network%20was%20banned%20on%20charges%20of%20blasphemy%20in%20late%202019%2C%20after%20conservatives%20took%20issue%20with%20its%20fouryear-old%20report%20on%20radicalization.%20Demonstrations%20across%20the%20country%20called%20for%20the%20authors%20to%20be%20executed%2C%20as%20the%20Adhaalath-dominated%20Islamic%20ministry%20declared%20them%20apostates%20who%20deserved%20the%20death%20penalty%20and%20forced%20them%20into%20exile%2C%20where%20they%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20in%202021%20to%20criminalize%20just%20this%20kind%20of%20takfiri%20rhetoric%20as%20hate%20speech%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20the%20term%20laadheenee%2C%20met%20ferocious%20opposition%2C%20with%20conservative%20networks%20labelling%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Secular%20Bill%E2%80%99.%20The%20MP%20who%20presented%20it%20was%20bombarded%20with%20death%20threats%2C%20and%20the%20bill%20was%20watered%20down.%20DDCom%20announced%20on%20the%20seventh%20anniversary%20of%20Riz%E2%80%99s%20disappearance%20that%20they%20had%20started%20work%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20witness%20protection%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20murder%20trial%20of%20Yameen%20Rasheed%2C%20after%20agonizingly%20slow%20progress%2C%20life%20sentences%20were%20handed%20to%20two%20men%20in%20early%202022%3A%20twenty-one-year-old%20Ismail%20Haisham%20Rasheed%20and%20twenty-two-year-old%20Ahmed%20Zihan%20Ismail.%20Four%20more%20were%20acquitted%2C%20and%20the%20family%20continues%20to%20press%20for%20the%20ringleaders%20to%20be%20brought%20to%20justice.%20In%20Riz%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20more%20foreign%20investigators%20were%20eventually%20brought%20in%2C%20and%20three%20men%20were%20arrested%20in%20July%202022%3A%20the%20alleged%20gang%20leaders%20Ahmed%20%E2%80%98Gatu%E2%80%99%20Muaz%20and%20Ahmed%20%E2%80%98Ahandu%E2%80%99%20Ismail%20as%20well%20as%20the%20man%20seen%20following%20both%20Riz%20and%20Yameen%2C%20Ismail%20Abdul%20Raheem.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20all%20are%20awaiting%20trial%20for%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%20DDCom%20alleged%20one%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20had%20met%20with%20Raees%20Yameen%2C%20receiving%20assistance%20to%20join%20fellow%20suspects%20in%20Syria%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20rejected%20by%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20225px)%2085vw%2C%20225px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fw