n%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20intend%20to%20do%20with%20ICSE.%20We%20want%20to%20give%20an%20opportunity%20for%20stakeholders%20and%20students%20to%20come%20together%20to%20encourage%20collective%20action%20and%20share%20ideas%20about%20fighting%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducation%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20climate%20transformation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20number%20of%20students%20participated%20in%20ICSE%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329402%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20students%20participated%20in%20ICSE%202022%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICSE%202023%20theme%20is%20%E2%80%98Educating%20for%20Climate%20Action%20and%20Sustainability%E2%80%99.%20It%20will%20take%20place%20from%2019%20and%C2%A0%2020%20September%202023%20at%20India%20Habitat%20Centre%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20conference%20will%20bring%20together%20professionals%2C%20educators%2C%20leaders%2C%20policymakers%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20students%20to%20collaborate%20on%20clima