tres%20from%20our%20factory%20and%20on%20three%20elevations.%20We%20decided%20not%20to%20touch%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20it%20and%20instead%20build%20our%20home%20around%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20on%20three%20levels%2C%20the%20house%20has%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20three%20bathrooms%2C%20one%20parlour%20room%20and%20a%20living%20room.%20Along%20with%20a%20dining%20room%20and%20a%20kitchen%2C%20it%20also%20has%20a%20pantry%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20a%20library%20and%20a%20lounge.%20The%20house%20has%20its%20own%20storeroom%2C%20an%20attic%2C%20and%20quarters%20for%20domestic%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20shape%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20land%20and%20decided%20to%20not%20level%20it.%20The%20house%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20does%20not%20look%20like%20an%20eyesore%20on%20the%20beautiful%20hill.%20Instead%2C%20it%20blends%20with%20nature%20and%20actually%20looks%20like%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20philosophy%20of%20the%20couple%20behind%20building%20the%20house%20was%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20efficient%2C%20cosy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187566%2Fchennai-architect-sustainable-homes-eco-friendly-construction-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20nature-friendly.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20the%20sole%20designers%20of%20the%20house.%20We%20did%20everything%20from%20scratch.%20We%20wanted%20the%20house%20to%20be%20comfortable%20and%20nature-friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-3-1693576553.jpg%5C%22%20width%